*   **PDM (Product Data Management):**
    *   [assembly.ts](file:///Users/cristiankalexai/Progetti/standlo.com/functions/src/choreography/assembly.ts) (Requires the new `batch` gateway action)
    *   [bundle.ts](file:///Users/cristiankalexai/Progetti/standlo.com/functions/src/choreography/bundle.ts) (Requires the new `batch` gateway action)
